{"type": "article", "id": 26287, "title": "歌唱鸟家饰", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-03T06:50:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152456p9sn6STMXcA85iWt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个名为间关（JinGoo）的家饰由来自台湾的产品设计团队大器创意（<a href=\"http://daqiconcept.com/\" target=\"_blank\">DAQI CONCEPT</a>）设计研发。“间关”一词在古代被用来形容宛转的鸟啼声，而在养鸟文化里，鸟笼就好像是文人雅士的必备家饰。大器将东方传统的家饰鸟笼概念和气氛灯光、蓝牙音响结合在了一起，不仅可以作为家饰增添居家氛围，也是一个用音乐创造更好气氛的“歌唱鸟”。你可以在 <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/jingoo-transform-your-space-with-music-and-light#/\">Indiegogo</a> 上了解更多信息，参与众筹的最低早鸟价为 179 美元。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152454Lvh4bIGgCwHM0kOl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152454wRXNUdvcI7PH0EnB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152455Zj4soiFdJv9MwUB5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021524557OWKyQdl9sAqXIZj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}